&lt;p&gt;We would use nodemon to run our backend code&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class="highlight js-code-highlight"&gt;
&lt;pre class="highlight shell"&gt;&lt;code&gt;nodemon index.js
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

