&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://media2.dev.to/dynamic/image/width=800%2Cheight=%2Cfit=scale-down%2Cgravity=auto%2Cformat=auto/https%3A%2F%2Fdev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fuploads%2Farticles%2Fimp0z8k7uk4h2o4e53r5.png" class="article-body-image-wrapper"&gt;&lt;img src="https://media2.dev.to/dynamic/image/width=800%2Cheight=%2Cfit=scale-down%2Cgravity=auto%2Cformat=auto/https%3A%2F%2Fdev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fuploads%2Farticles%2Fimp0z8k7uk4h2o4e53r5.png" alt="running nodemon on bash" width="776" height="150"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Note: Ctrl+C to stop the server&lt;/p&gt;

