&lt;h2&gt;


Adjustment Guide by Project Scale
&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;


Small Scale (1-2 months)
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tasks That Can Be Skipped&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

