&lt;p&gt;Notice that I added the role there. There is also a new hook called useEnhancedQueryKey. It's very simple, and I will show it soon. I also changed the way of passing the fetch function. Now useEnhancedQuery accepts an endpoint (which is a callback with the shop passed and returning a string). I did that because it's now easier to pass new parameters straight away to the client (fetch wrapper) function. Now let's see &lt;code&gt;useEnhancedQueryKey&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;br&gt;
